text: Marko Tanasić (born December 2,1964) is a retired Serbian football midfielder.Weltfussball He got 38 Eliteserien games in Norway with Strømsgodset, and was also on their losing team in the 1997 Norwegian Football Cup Final. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Serbian footballers Category:FK Spartak Subotica players Category:Knattspyrnudeild Keflavík players Category:Strømsgodset Toppfotball players Category:Sandefjord Fotball players Category:Association football midfielders Category:Serbian expatriate footballers Category:Expatriate footballers in Iceland Category:Serbian expatriate sportspeople in Iceland Category:Expatriate footballers in Norway Category:Serbian expatriate sportspeople in Norway Category:Eliteserien players Category:Norwegian First Division players
